name: 'By the light of the moon' poster print
description:
A digital print of an original illustration painted in acrylic paint on canvas. 
Printed on white 160gsm silk poster paper. Print measures 
21x 29cm (A4). 
( Also available in A3 size)

Will be sent to you signed on the back and enclosed in a waterproof sleeve and a hardback envelope to ensure it reaches you safe and sound.

Fell free to contact me if you have any questions!
